rows.label: qev065103_MSG0001
rows.name: You will not touch me with those filthy hands![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065103_MSG0002
rows.name:
I am Fortun, queen of the Definians and keeper of the
galaxy's wisdom since time immemorial. You will act
as befits a lesser being in my presence.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065103_SEL0011
rows.name: Treat Fortun in a manner befitting royalty.

rows.label: qev065103_SEL0021
rows.name: Drag Fortun along like a sack of potatoes.

rows.label: qev065103_MSG0003
rows.name:
Hmm. It seems you are at least capable of some form
of intelligent thought.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065103_MSG0004
rows.name:
Then I will not resist, for now.
Take me where you will.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065103_MSG0005
rows.name:
Truthfully, it matters not. In time, you will know death
at the hands of my daughters.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065103_MSG0006
rows.name:
Fitting behavior for such a primitive creature.
Your foolishness has incurred my wrath.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065103_MSG0007
rows.name:
[ST:playername ], is it? In time, you will meet
death at the hands of my daughters. As will your
friends, your acquaintances, and everyone you know.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065103_MSG0008
rows.name:
Ha ha! You are surprised? There is nothing in all of
space that escapes my knowing gaze.[ST:wait ]
